ISLAMABAD, Aug 14 (APP): Prime Minister Shehbaz Sharif Sunday congratulated Ministry of Information and Broadcasting led by Marriyum Aurangzeb, Inter Services Public Relations and all the institutions concerned for holding magnificent ceremonies in connection with the 75th Independence Day celebrations.
In a tweet on social media platform Twitter, he said, “the living nations never let their younger generation forget about their identity and on this day you all ensured that this message gets across.”
